    <description>This flow sends an email notification to the Investment Performance team when the field Benchmark Name is filled in during the Proposal phase of a PMT project.
The field must be completed by the Product Specialist (PS) team and their phase (Proposal) must be validated.
The objective is to prompt the Investment Performance team to create and/or associate the official benchmark to the corresponding PMT record.</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
